Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.38,0:00:05.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's time for the Sibylla Aurea Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.53,0:00:11.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monthly! ADR Bulletin Special{\i0}\N{\i1}Pair Versus Pair Competition!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:11.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:16.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,...to determine which pair is worthy\Nof being called "Golden Priestesses"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:16.22,Signs,,0,0,0,,Mamina\NRIKA MORINAGA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:21.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and you'll be\Ncompeting in teams of two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:24.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,After the last round, the pair,\Nor team, with the most points...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:29.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...will receive an extremely\Nvaluable prize! Do your best, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:36.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's have each member\Nintroduce herself and their pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:40.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Michi Niino, and I play Aer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:42.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I play Neviril...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.42,0:00:46.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,I play Neviril.\NMy name is Rieko Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:50.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,The pair's name is Lilies of the Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:53.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Ami Koshimizu,\Nand I play Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:57.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,I play Kaim. Michiko Hosokoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.04,0:00:57.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:00.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our pair's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:02.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the Mangoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Mamiko Noto, and I play Rimone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:08.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mikako Takahashi. I play Roatreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:10.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our pair's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:13.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Monotone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:14.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.07,0:01:15.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.73,0:01:17.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:20.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm Michiru Aizawa, and I play Floe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:24.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um... Alty, right?\NI'm Megumi Toyoguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.24,0:01:25.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Our pair's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:28.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Team Green!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:31.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Copycats! Copycats!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:33.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rip-off! Rip-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:36.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Copycats? Yes, but please\Nroot for us anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.31,0:01:41.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, so here they are...\Nthe contestants of this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:52.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's the best couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:54.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun Compatibility Test!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:03.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,So let's start with\Na simple word association game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:06.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll give you\Na keyword related to Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:09.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and you each write down\Nwhatever comes to mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:12.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,...using those writing boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:17.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Points will be awarded if both\Nteam members give the same answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:22.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll give you the first\Nkeyword now, and it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:27.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,In your opinion, what's the first\Nstep in becoming an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:30.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, everybody!\NGet your answers ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun related?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:42.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've been abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,From the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:46.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Becoming an adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:49.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,It depends if we keep\Nthe story in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Becoming an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,How are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:56.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ding-ding-ding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, now that time's up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:04.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's hear how Ms. Niino and\NMs. Takahashi, the Lilies, answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please show us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:06.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:13.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Pretty long! When you start your first\Njob, start making your own money...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:16.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like a part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:18.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Very realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:20.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's so realistic. A part-time job...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,She even wrote it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:26.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then let's see your answer, Rieko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:29.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Love{\i0}\NTa-da... Totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:35.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's like you're really holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:35.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,But still, they're both mature answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:36.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:40.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,The answers are\Ntotally different, so no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:46.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, next up... Ami-chan\Nand Michiko-san, the Mangoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:50.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why don't you show us at\Nthe same time? Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:54.82,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shopping alone (running first errand){\i0}\N{\i1}Going shopping by yourself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:57.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Running your first errand too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're definitely a good match, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:13.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next up, Mamiko-san and\NMeguko-chan, the Monotones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:15.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:20.34,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}20 years old Alcohol{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:26.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's "you can turn\N20 after you drink alcohol"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:30.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can drink alcohol\Nafter you turn 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:39.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, um, nothing doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:42.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,No good, no good.\NWrong answer, wrong answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:46.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.\NIt's Michiru-chan and Megu-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:49.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go, green team. Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:52.85,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}First Kiss (Smack!) Alcohol{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:52.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should pair up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:55.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:59.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,I knew we'd agree on something...\NAnd it had to be this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:02.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I guess it's\Nthe generation gap or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yup, to be brutally honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all, you can't...\NYou can't yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:10.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I can't drink yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another no-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:14.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then on to the next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:17.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Question number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:25.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,What makes a woman beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:26.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:30.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you please.\NWrite it down, write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay! We're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:40.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, which page\Ndid I write my answer on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,You wrote a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:45.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready? All right, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:48.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the Lilies again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:51.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Show us your answers.\NReady, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:56.28,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never bending her will to the very end!{\i0}\N{\i1}Her purity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.80,0:05:58.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,No good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, next. The Mangoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:09.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,To always be smiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:11.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, they're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Smiles equal kindness, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't think they're equal at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:24.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,No good, no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next, the Monotones!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:34.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Content.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, mine means "outside"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:43.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,So as long as it looks good\Non the outside, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:45.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:49.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,So we should write\Nthe opposite thing from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:54.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's another "no-good" answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, Team Green next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:00.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:04.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neviril-sama Being in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:04.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,What kind of answer is that? You\Nokay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:09.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,I tried every which way\Nto come up with a teen's answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:10.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,An answer that evokes youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's up with that answer?\NNeviril-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because she's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:19.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,"All you have to be is beautiful."\N("Utsukushikereba soredeii.")
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:20.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,The theme song.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, it is a typical Floe answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I guess for this corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,...l'll give the Mangoes\N10,000 points or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,10,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,So anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:41.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's it for\Nthe Simoun Compatibility Test!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:53.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Super-Difficult Simoun Cult Quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:59.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, so the rules are very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:02.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a quiz all about\Nwhat happens in the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:06.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll read show-related questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:10.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and I'd like you to write your\Nanswers on the writing boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:14.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,So let's get started. Question one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:17.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Before their first flight in episode\None...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:22.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,...how many times did\NNeviril and Amuria kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:26.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that is super difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Before their first flight in episode\None...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:32.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,...how many times did\NNeviril and Amuria kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:35.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Before their flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:48.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Five, four, three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chu-chu, chu-chu-chu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:54.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,What kind of a sound effect was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:59.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd make it more quizlike.\NEach team, show your answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:02.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,First up, the Lilies. Ready, set, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:07.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:07.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Which teams answered "three times"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:13.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, can we get extra points for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:15.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,That side interests me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:17.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Listen, this isn't\Na manga-drawing class, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:29.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, Monotones, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ta-da.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,1.5 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:37.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where does the 0.5 come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:37.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wrong, wrong, wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,If they stopped at the last second...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,We averaged it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:49.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, the correct answer is twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:56.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,But we're closest! We're closest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:59.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're closer than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,You all said it was three times!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:11.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since you two were so cute getting\Nall worked up, I'll give you points.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:21.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Enough! They told me I could\Nbe biased and partial, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:23.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:27.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,In episode two, when Neviril\Nwas wearing civilian clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,...what color was her bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.51,0:10:33.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,A Neviril question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Answer, answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:36.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Think, think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:37.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, her hair's pink, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:54.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Five, four, three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:57.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kon-kon-kon-kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:01.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that?\NIt was just a whisper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:05.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start\Nwith Team Lilies' answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ready, set, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:09.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,How elegant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:15.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Look at that smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:15.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,She's brimming with confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:18.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,If she gets this one wrong,\Nit's going to be funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:21.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril's answer is purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:29.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, the Mangoes next. Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:33.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go! An orangish-brownish color.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,An orangish-brownish color?\NWhich is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, it's kind of subtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,More of which?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:40.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mottled!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mean marbled?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:47.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,In keeping with the Simoun theme...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please accept our answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Then next...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:50.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,H-How cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:53.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,To the next answer. Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go-go-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,A pink flower pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:00.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Her hair's pink, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:04.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since her hair's pink,\Nshe decides to color coordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:08.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,When she has to ponder\Nbecoming a man or woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:11.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Since I've got pink hair,\Nlet's go with a flower pattern!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:15.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,"It won't do without it."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:19.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's very typical.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:22.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,On to the next team,\NTeam Green. Ready, set...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:23.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Go. Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:24.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:29.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,I seem to remember it was\Na darkish color, like purple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:32.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, not brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:36.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:38.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,The correct answer is brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:43.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on! Hey, MC!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:48.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Orangish-brownish" isn't brown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:48.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think it could look orange too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim! Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:08.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I'm counting that\Nas a correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's it for\Nthe Super-Difficult Cult Quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:21.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Simoun Anything and\NEverything Case Files.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:28.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, in this corner,\NI'll ask you to answer questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:32.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,...about inside stories,\Nthings that happened during ADR.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,So it's a kiss-and-tell contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:38.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll pick a question out of this box...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Written by you before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:45.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I'll start drawing, and I'd like\Nto discuss these stories with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm agreeing with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:51.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,The keyword... Okay, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:58.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Surprised to be in a place where\Nwomen gave their all playing men!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:59.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:01.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Meguko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:07.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right from episode one, everyone\Ndid a valiant job playing old men...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:11.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,...throwing themselves into it,\Nand I was very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:16.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,When they did the first session,\Nyou could hear laughter in the booth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,The staff was cracking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:26.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because usually, having a girl's voice\Ncoming out of an old guy's mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:30.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,It never happened in anime till now.\NIt shouldn't ever happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:34.98,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Government Official{\i0}\N{\i1}Voiced by Megumi Toyoguchi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:34.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Your daughter is\Nan outstanding pilot, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:38.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we signed up for old guys,\Nwe'd say, "This one!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:40.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like the somewhat chubby one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:46.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wish they'd credit us\Nfor the old guys we played.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:50.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're not old guys! Like "soldier"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:56.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:15:00.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Basically, I have very few lines.\NAnd no ad libs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:07.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,You see, in the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:12.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,The thing is... basically,\NRimone doesn't have a lot of dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had quite a few ad libbed lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:21.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,But one by one, they'd say,\N"Not needed, not needed, not needed."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:25.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,So she hardly had dialogue.\NOnly a line or two when she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:30.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I thought, "I wish I could\Ntalk as much as everyone else."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was my secret dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Not that it was accidental...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,They pretty much delete everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:41.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,So in the nondialogue\Nparts of the script...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:44.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like when they write "turns around"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:46.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,They'd normally write "ad lib"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:50.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,But as far as this show, they're like,\N"We don't need this. Cross that out."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:55.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,But when you think you don't\Nhave any lines, they add something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:58.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like to turn around violently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:15:59.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Like, "Hah!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hard to know\Nwhere to draw the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.51,0:16:06.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,And sometimes they throw\Nland mines like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:09.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Set traps for you in your path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:12.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:24.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea Battle\NPair Versus Pair Competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Here are the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:36.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, which team will\Nclaim the "Golden Priestess" title?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:41.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've taken the liberty of deciding,\Nand it's a biased and partial decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:46.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, well, what did\Nyou think of the games?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun? Was it hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.96,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was really motivated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:53.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I drew some pictures too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:55.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:58.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I have a feeling we're gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did you score?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:03.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,The green in your clothes\Nis even more dazzling now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:06.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,You didn't get any points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:10.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let me\Nannounce the winning team!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:13.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,The winners are the Mangoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:17.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Winners{\i0}\N{\i1}The Mangoes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:17.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, you put up a good fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,As expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:24.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and you performed well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:29.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now then, the Mangoes will be\Npresented with this Simoun candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Kaim...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:38.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:42.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please shower your\Nkisses on this candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Kaim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:53.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:59.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, so the Mangoes\Nended up winning today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:02.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,And I'm glad we all got\Nto have a good time today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.57,0:18:05.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please keep watching Simoun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:07.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please keep watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,So the Sibylla Aurea Battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simoun... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:17.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Sibylla Aurea Battle\NPair Versus Pair Competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:20.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's all, folks! Everyone, bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:26.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
